Cell["\<\
The above ZZ interaction is equivalent to the following combination of CNOT \
and single-qubit rotation:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->248952008,ExpressionUUID->"262e683a-7cff-4d3d-b8c6-aa102e1ea360"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
